reviewText: Bought this for my daughter for homeschooling and she is really learning a lot.

Awesome program. Comes with a dvd and cd rom. I had not troubles watching the cd on my computer using windows media player. I was also able to download the worksheets and answer guide. This does a great job of not teaching too fast or slow. Perfect for the homeschooling family. My kids can watch these in the car on the go. I only wish they had other grades.
good teaching, but why randomly do fifth grade?  i wish i could find this series specifically for 6th grade.
No indication of what program these discs run under and nothing I have will open them. :(
